   <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0">
    To do the sign "FOR," touch your forehead and swing the tip of your finger 
	forward.
    <br/>
   </p>
   <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0">
    FOR:
    <br/>
    <img border="0" src="/images/for.gif" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto" width="480"/>
